    "sr": false,
    "shortDescription": "<p>You can focus upon a single point within line of sight and discern if the terrain or geographic features of that point are illusory. This ability allows you a Will save to disbelieve a terrain-affecting illusion (glamer) effect from range as though you had interacted with it. In addition to affecting such spells as <i>hallucinatory terrain</i> and <i>mirage arcana</i>, this spell also allows you to disbelieve naturally occurring mirages.</p>"
